      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BARBARY TALES (4) resumes from a spell of six-and-a-half months after closing off last campaign in good form, scoring at her last appearance over 2200m at Launceston. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Will have plenty of admirers. IMPERIAL LAZ NZ (2) registered a strong performance last start when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 2090m at this track. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Meets a comparable field and he is a strong winning hope. MCMAYHEM (1) got the prize two runs back then his luck changed last time when he broke and finished 10 metres back in fourth over 1680m at Launceston. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Live chance in a similar assignment. ONE BIG SHEW (5) last appeared when tenth over 2200m at Launceston seven months ago. Expect a better effort to kick off this prep.",
